programme.desc: Arizona Cardinals v Denver Broncos (Kick-off 1.20am). Coverage of the match between the respective NFC West and AFC West sides, which takes place at State Farm Stadium in Phoenix. This is the opening fixture in week seven, and even at this early juncture a victory could do little to improve the hosts chances of reaching the play-offs this season, after they began the campaign with a number of consecutive losses. One ray of hope for Cardinals fans has been the introduction of rookie quarterback Josh Rosen, who was drafted from UCLA Bruins in the off-season, and appears to be a bright prospect for the future, who could inspire them to a reversal of fortunes.

programme.title: Razor Dobbs Alive

programme.title: The Ultimate Hunt
